        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="c-基础入门："><a href="#c-基础入门：" class="headerlink" title="c++基础入门："></a><strong>c++基础入门：</strong></h2><p><em><strong>一、c++第一个程序</strong></em></p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span>  <span class="meta-string">&quot;iostream&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;hello world! &lt;&lt;endl;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">systeam(&quot;</span>pause<span class="string">&quot;);    //可以不要</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">return 0;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em><strong>二、注释</strong></em>（注释不被执行或运行）<br><strong>1：单行注释</strong><br>// 内容</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">在这里插入代码片</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//内容</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>2：多行注释</strong><br>/*  内容  */</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">在这里插入代码片</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/* 内容 */</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em><strong>三、变量和常量</strong></em><br><strong>1：变量</strong></p><blockquote><p>作用：给一段指定的内存空间起名，方便操作这段内存.</p></blockquote><p>01：语法： 数据类型    变量名=初始值;</p><blockquote><p>变量意义：变量名取代地址编号、方便我们管理内存空间.</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//变量的定义</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//语法：数据类型  变量名 =初始化;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> a=<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;a=&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; a &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">system</span>(<span class="string">&quot;pause&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> ;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>2：常量</strong></p><blockquote><p>作用：用于记录程序中不可更改的数据.</p><p>#define语法：#define  常量名   常量值（通常在文件上定义，表示一个常量）.</p><p>const修饰常量：const 数据类型  变量名 =变量值 （通常在变量定义前面加关键字const、修饰该变量为常量、不可修改）.</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//常量的定义方式：</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//1、#define 宏常量</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//2、const修饰变量</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">define</span> Day 7</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//Day=14;//错误，Day是常量，一旦修改就会报错.</span></span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;一周共有：&quot;</span>&lt;&lt; Day &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot; 天&quot;</span> &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//const修饰变量</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="keyword">int</span> month=<span class="number">12</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// month=12;  </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*错误，加上const修饰变量也称为常量，不能改变值，</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">不加const可以改值，month=12正确的*/</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;一年总共有：&quot;</span>&lt;&lt; month &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;月份&quot;</span> &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">system</span>(<span class="string">&quot;pause&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em><strong>四、关键字</strong></em></p><blockquote><p>作用：关键字是c++中预先保留的单词（标识符）</p><p>注意：在定义变量或常量的时候，不能用关键字来命名.</p></blockquote><p><strong>c++关键字如下：（单词已经被编译器系统用了，不能在用）</strong><br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/190894be7d9c4c579db7e7a647609d1c.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAQ1gzMDBv,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16#pic_center" alt="在这里插入图片描述"><br><em><strong>五、标识符命名规则</strong></em><br><em>作用：c++规定给标识符（变量、常量）命名时，有自己的规则.</em></p><blockquote><p>规则——》01：标识符不能是关键字. 02：标识符只能由字母、数字、下划线组成. 03：要以字母或下划线开头. 04：标识符中字母区分大小写.</p></blockquote><p><em>| 建议：给标识符命名时，争取做到见名知意的效果，方便自己和他人的阅读.</em></p><hr><h2 id="数据类型："><a href="#数据类型：" class="headerlink" title="数据类型："></a><em><strong>数据类型：</strong></em></h2><p>规则：c++规则在创建一个变量或者常量时，必须要指定出相应的数据类型，否则无法给变量分配内存.</p><p><em><strong>一、整型</strong></em></p><blockquote><p>作用：整型变量表示的是整型类型的数据.</p><p>意义：给变量分配合适的内存空间.</p></blockquote><p><strong>c++中能够表示整型的类型有有以下几种方式：</strong><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/5b43de94c3c54f8982f8af6dfeaadefe.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAQ1gzMDBv,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16#pic_center" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">mian</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//整型</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//1、短整型  （-32768~32767）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//short num1=32767;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//2、短整型 </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//int num2=10;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//3、长整型</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">long</span> num3=<span class="number">10</span>；</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//4、长长整型</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">long</span> <span class="keyword">long</span> num4=<span class="number">10</span>；</span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;num1=&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;num1&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;num2=&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;num2&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;num3=&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;num3&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;num4=&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;num4&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em><strong>二、sizeof关键字</strong></em></p><blockquote><p>作用：利用sizeof关键字可以统计数据类型所占内存大小.</p><p>   语法：sizeof（数据类型/变量）<br>   占用空间：用（字节）来表示</p></blockquote><p><strong>例如：</strong></p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> num1=<span class="number">10</span>;<span class="comment">//num1为变量也可以放入sizeof（变量）里面.</span></span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;short 类型多占内存空间为：&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;<span class="built_in"><span class="keyword">sizeof</span></span>(<span class="keyword">short</span>)&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;int 类型多占内存空间为：&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;<span class="built_in"><span class="keyword">sizeof</span></span>(<span class="keyword">int</span>)&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;long 类型多占内存空间为：&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;<span class="built_in"><span class="keyword">sizeof</span></span>(<span class="keyword">long</span>)&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;long long 类型多占内存空间为：&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;<span class="built_in"><span class="keyword">sizeof</span></span>(<span class="keyword">long</span> <span class="keyword">long</span>)&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//整型大小比较</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//short &lt; int &lt; =long &lt; = long long</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">system</span>(<span class="string">&quot;pause&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>| 结论：short &lt; int &lt; = long &lt; = long long</strong></p><p><em><strong>三、实型（浮点型）</strong></em></p><blockquote><p>作用：用来表示小数.<br>      浮点型变量分为两种：<br>      1、单精度float<br>      2、双精度double</p></blockquote><p>| 注意：两者的区别在于表示的有效数字范围不同。</p><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/d0b56807cd214ba6b7a3346ce6657ac5.png#pic_center" alt="在这里插入图片描述"><br>例如：</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#inlcude <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//默认情况下、输出一个小数、会显示出6位有效数字.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*单精度float、双精度double*/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">float</span>  f1=<span class="number">3.14f</span>;  <span class="comment">//后面要加一个f，因为不加会默认是double类型.</span></span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;f1=:&quot;</span>&lt;&lt; f1 &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">double</span>  d1=<span class="number">3.14</span>;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;d1=:&quot;</span>&lt;&lt; d1 &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//float和double占用内存空间：</span></span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;float 占用内存空间为：&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;<span class="keyword">sizeof</span>（<span class="keyword">float</span>）&lt;&lt;endl;<span class="comment">//4字节</span></span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;double 占用内存空间为：&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;<span class="keyword">sizeof</span>（<span class="keyword">double</span>）&lt;&lt;endl;<span class="comment">//8字节</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//科学计数法</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">float</span> f2 =<span class="number">3e2</span>;   <span class="comment">//3*10^2;</span></span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;f2=&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;f2&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"> <span class="keyword">float</span> f3 =<span class="number">3e-2</span>;  <span class="comment">//3*10^2;</span></span><br><span class="line"> cout &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;f3=&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;f3&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">system</span>(<span class="string">&quot;pause&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em><strong>四、字符型</strong></em></p><blockquote><p>作用：字符型变量用于显示单个字符<br>       语法：char    ch   =‘a’；</p></blockquote><p>| 注意1：在显示字符型变量时、用单引号将字符型括起来、不能用双引号.<br>| 注意2：单引号内只能有一个字符，不可以是字符串.</p><p>1：c和c++中字符型变量只能占用1个字节。<br>2：字符型变量并不是把字符本身放到内存中存储，而是将对应的ASCll编码放入到内存单元</p><p>例如：</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//1、字符型变量创建方式</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">char</span> ch=<span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; ch &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//2、字符型变量所占内存大小</span></span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;char字符型所占的变量内存：&quot;</span> &lt;&lt;<span class="built_in"><span class="keyword">sizeof</span></span>(<span class="keyword">char</span>) &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//3、字符型变量常见错误</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//char ch2=&quot;b&quot;; //错误1：创建字符型变量时候、不能用单引号.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//char ch2=&#x27;absd&#x27;；//错误：创建字符型变量时候、单引号内只能有一个字符.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//4、字符型变量对应ASCll编码</span></span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;(<span class="keyword">int</span>)ch &lt;&lt;end;<span class="comment">//查看字符型a对应的ASCll编码，把字符型转化为整型让我们看到.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">system</span>(<span class="string">&quot;pause&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>ASCll编码：<img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/2a761ffac4404576acb5cdebeb9eb525.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAQ1gzMDBv,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16#pic_center" alt="在这里插入图片描述"><br><em><strong>五、转义字符</strong></em></p><blockquote><p>作用：用于表示一些不能显示出来的ASCll字符<br>        现阶段我们常用的转义字符有：1、\n    2、 \   (两个反斜杠就会输出一个反斜杠） 3、  \t<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/8bfd2d83a34c4c3983f21b86e7024ec4.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA6I-c6bif5a2m6K6h566X5py6,size_14,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16#pic_center" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p></blockquote><p>例如：</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">mian</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//转义字符</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//1、换行符 \n </span></span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;hello world\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//2、反斜杠 \\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">cout&lt;&lt;&quot; \\ &quot;&lt;&lt;endl;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//3、水平制表符 \t   //(作用可以整齐输出数据)</span></span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;a\thello world&quot;</span> &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;aa\thello world&quot;</span> &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;aaa\thello world&quot;</span> &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">system</span>(<span class="string">&quot;pause&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em><strong>六、字符串型</strong></em></p><blockquote><p>作用：用于表示一串字符.</p></blockquote><p><strong>两种方式：</strong><br>1、c语言风格字符串：char 变量名[ ]  = “字符串值”<br>例如：</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">mian</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//c语言字符串</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">char</span> str[]=<span class="string">&quot;hello world&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; str &lt;&lt;<span class="built_in">endl</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>| 注意：c风格的字符串要用双引号括起来.</p></blockquote><p>1、c++风格字符串：string   变量名  =“字符串值”<br>例如：</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;string&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="comment">/*用c++风格字符串时候，要包含这个头文件，但是版本更新现在不要了.*/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">mian</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//c++风格字符串</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*包含头文件 ，现在可以不要头文件 #include &lt;string&gt;*/</span></span><br><span class="line">string   str=<span class="string">&quot;hello world&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;str&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">system</span>(<span class="string">&quot;pause&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em><strong>七、布尔类型 bool</strong></em></p><blockquote><p>作用：布尔数据类型代表真或假的值<br>       bool类型只有两个值：<br>       1、true …真（本质是1）<br>       2、false …假 （本质是0）<br>       bool类型占1字节大小</p></blockquote><p>例如：</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">mian</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//1、创建bool数据类型</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">bool</span> mall=<span class="literal">true</span>;  <span class="comment">//true代表真</span></span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; <span class="literal">true</span> &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">mall=<span class="literal">false</span>; <span class="comment">//false代表假</span></span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;<span class="literal">false</span> &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//2、查看bool类型所占内存空间</span></span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;bool类型所占内存空间为：&quot;</span> &lt;&lt;<span class="built_in"><span class="keyword">sizeof</span></span>(<span class="keyword">bool</span>) &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">system</span>(<span class="string">&quot;pause&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em><strong>八、数据的输入</strong></em></p><blockquote><p>作用：用于从键盘获取数据.<br>          关键字：cin<br>          语法：cin &gt;&gt;变量</p></blockquote><p>例如：</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">uisng <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">mian</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//1、整型</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> a=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;请输入整型变量a赋值：&quot;</span> &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">cin&gt;&gt;a;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;整型变量a=&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; a &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//2、浮点型</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">float</span> f=<span class="number">3.14f</span>;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;请输入浮点型变量f赋值：&quot;</span> &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">cin &gt;&gt;f;</span><br><span class="line">cout  &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;浮点型变量f=&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; f &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//3、字符型</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">char</span> ch=<span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;请输入字符型变量赋值：&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">cin&gt;&gt;ch;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;字符型变量ch=&quot;</span>&lt;&lt; ch &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//4、字符串</span></span><br><span class="line">string str = <span class="string">&quot; 123&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;请输入字符串变量赋值：&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">cin&gt;&gt;str;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;字符串变量str=&quot;</span>&lt;&lt; str &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//5、布尔型</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">bool</span> flag=<span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;请输入布尔型变量赋值：&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">cin&gt;&gt;flag;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;布尔型变量f=&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; flag &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">system</span>(<span class="string">&quot;pause&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="运算符："><a href="#运算符：" class="headerlink" title="运算符："></a><em><strong>运算符：</strong></em></h2><blockquote><p>作用：用于执行代码的运算</p></blockquote><p>有几种类运算符：<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/30b5c197cc5440e9ad6e4f39a31f0d28.png#pic_center" alt="在这里插入图片描述"><br><em><strong>一、算术运算符</strong></em></p><blockquote><p>作用：用于处理四则运算</p></blockquote><p>算术运算符包括以下符号：<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/fc9ce30829824d289056d0586d89fac7.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA6I-c6bif5a2m6K6h566X5py6,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16#pic_center" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">intmain</span>()</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//加减乘除</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> a=<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> b=<span class="number">3</span>;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; a+b &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; a-b &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; a*b &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; a/<span class="number">3</span> &lt;&lt;endl; <span class="comment">//两个整数相除，结果依然是整数，将小数部分除去.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 10/0 错误分母不可以等于0.</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//两个小数可以相除</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">double</span> d=<span class="number">0.5</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">double</span> d2=<span class="number">0.25</span>;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;d/d2&lt;&lt;endl; <span class="comment">//运算的结果也可以是小数.</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//取模运算本质 就是求余数.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> a1=<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> a2=<span class="number">3</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//两个数相除数不可以为0，所以也做不了取模运算.</span></span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;a1%a2&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//两个小数是不可以做取模运算的.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">double</span> d1=<span class="number">3.14</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">double</span>  d2=<span class="number">1.1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; d1%d2 &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//1、前置递增</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> a=<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">++a; <span class="comment">//让变量+1</span></span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;a=&quot;</span> &lt;&lt;a&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//2、后置递增</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> b=<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">b++;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;b=&quot;</span> &lt;&lt;b&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//3、前置和后置的区别</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//前置递增 先让变量+1 然后进行表达式运算</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> a2 =<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> b2 =++a2*<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;a2=&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; a2 &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;b2=&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; b2 &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//后置递增 先进行表达式运算  然后在变量+1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> a3=<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> b3=a3++*<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;a3=&quot;</span> &lt;&lt;a3&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">cout  &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;b3=&quot;</span> &lt;&lt;b3 &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//前置递减和后置递减可以自己去写一下.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">system</span>(<span class="string">&quot;pause&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em><strong>二、赋值运算符</strong></em></p><blockquote><p>作用：用于将表达式的值赋值给变量.</p></blockquote><p>赋值运算符包含以下几个符号：<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/e4f19140754545b5b3c8b71ed9c88dee.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA6I-c6bif5a2m6K6h566X5py6,size_19,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16#pic_center" alt="在这里插入图片描述"><br>示例：</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">mian</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//赋值运算符</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// =</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> a=<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">a=<span class="number">100</span>;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;a=&quot;</span> &lt;&lt;a&lt;&lt;endl; <span class="comment">//结果为100.</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// +=</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> a=<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">a+=<span class="number">2</span>; <span class="comment">//a = a +2</span></span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;a=&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;a&lt;&lt;endl; <span class="comment">//结果为12.</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// -=</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> a=<span class="number">10</span>; </span><br><span class="line">a-=<span class="number">2</span>; <span class="comment">//a=a-2</span></span><br><span class="line">cout  &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;a=&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;a&lt;&lt;endl; <span class="comment">//结果为8.</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// *=</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> a=<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">a*=<span class="number">2</span>; <span class="comment">//a=a*2.</span></span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;a=&quot;</span> &lt;&lt;a&lt;&lt;endl; <span class="comment">//结果为20.</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// /=</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> a=<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">a/=<span class="number">2</span>; <span class="comment">// a=a/2.</span></span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;a=&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;a&lt;&lt;endl; <span class="comment">//结果为5.</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// %=</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> a=<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">a%=<span class="number">2</span>; <span class="comment">// a=a%2.</span></span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;a=&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;a&lt;&lt;endl; <span class="comment">// 结果为0.</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">system</span>(<span class="string">&quot;pause&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em><strong>三、比较运算符</strong></em></p><blockquote><p>作用：用于表达式的比较，并返回一个真值或假值.</p></blockquote><p>比较运算符有以下符号：<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/4eb33918ada44e6da4148973d0dc4571.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA6I-c6bif5a2m6K6h566X5py6,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16#pic_center" alt="在这里插入图片描述"><br>示例：</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//比较运算符</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//  ==</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> a=<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> b=<span class="number">20</span>;</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;(a==b)&lt;&lt;endl; <span class="comment">//加小括号因为，做一个优先级，先算小括号在算后面.</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//  !=</span></span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt;(a!=b)&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//  &gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; a&gt;b &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//  &lt; </span></span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; (a&lt;b) &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//  &gt;=</span></span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; (a&gt;=b) &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//  &lt;=</span></span><br><span class="line">cout  &lt;&lt; (a&lt;=b) &lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">system</span>(<span class="string">&quot;pause&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em><strong>四、逻辑运算符</strong></em></p><blockquote><p>作用：用于根据表达式的值返回真值或假值.</p></blockquote><p>逻辑运算符有以下符号：<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/51435ba6e609414295507d352d056a66.png#pic_center" alt="在这里插入图片描述"><br>示例：</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">mian</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//逻辑运算符   非   ！</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> a = <span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//在c++中，除了0都为真</span></span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; !a &lt;&lt;endl; <span class="comment">//结果为 0.</span></span><br><span class="line">cout  &lt;&lt; !!a &lt;&lt;endl; <span class="comment">//结果为 1.</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//逻辑运算符   与   &amp;&amp;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> a=<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> b=<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">cout  &lt;&lt;(a&amp;&amp;b) &lt;&lt;endl; <span class="comment">//结果为1.</span></span><br><span class="line">a=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">b=<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">cout  &lt;&lt;(a&amp;&amp;b) &lt;&lt;endl; <span class="comment">//结果为0.</span></span><br><span class="line">a=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">a=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">cout  &lt;&lt;(a&amp;&amp;b) &lt;&lt;endl; <span class="comment">//结果为0.</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="comment">//逻辑运算符   或   ||</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> a=<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> b=<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">cout  &lt;&lt;(a||b) &lt;&lt;endl <span class="comment">//结果为1.</span></span><br><span class="line">a=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">a=<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">cout  &lt;&lt;(a||b) &lt;&lt;endl <span class="comment">//结果为1.</span></span><br><span class="line">a=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">b=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">cout  &lt;&lt;(a||b) &lt;&lt;endl <span class="comment">//结果为0.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">system</span>(<span class="string">&quot;pause&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr>]]></content>
      
      
      
